## MVVM Pattern (CommunityToolkit.Mvvm)
```csharp
[ObservableObject]
public partial class ItemListViewModel
{
    private readonly IItemService _itemService;
    private readonly IConnectivity _connectivity;

    [ObservableProperty]
    [NotifyPropertyChangedFor(nameof(HasItems))]
    private ObservableCollection<ItemDto> _items = new();

    [ObservableProperty]
    private bool _isLoading;

    public bool HasItems => Items.Count > 0;

    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task LoadItemsAsync(CancellationToken ct)
    {
        IsLoading = true;
        try
        {
            var data = _connectivity.NetworkAccess == NetworkAccess.Internet
                ? await _itemService.GetFromApiAsync(ct)
                : await _itemService.GetFromLocalAsync(ct);
            Items = new ObservableCollection<ItemDto>(data);
        }
        finally { IsLoading = false; }
    }
}
```

## Offline-First Architecture

### Delta Sync Engine
```csharp
public class SyncEngine
{
    // 1. Pull: server'dan son sync'ten bu yana degisenleri al
    public async Task PullAsync(CancellationToken ct)
    {
        var lastSync = await _localDb.GetLastSyncTimestamp();
        var changes = await _api.GetChangesAsync(lastSync, ct);
        await _localDb.ApplyRemoteChanges(changes);
        await _localDb.SetLastSyncTimestamp(DateTime.UtcNow);
    }

    // 2. Push: lokal degisiklikleri server'a gonder
    public async Task PushAsync(CancellationToken ct)
    {
        var pending = await _localDb.GetPendingChanges();
        foreach (var change in pending)
        {
            var result = await _api.SyncChangeAsync(change, ct);
            if (result.IsSuccess)
                await _localDb.MarkAsSynced(change.Id);
            else if (result.IsConflict)
                await HandleConflict(change, result.ServerVersion);
        }
    }
}
```

### Conflict Resolution
```
Strateji Secimi:
├── Last-Write-Wins (LWW): Basit, veri kaybi riski
├── Server-Wins: Server her zaman dogru (cogu senaryo)
├── Client-Wins: Offline oncelikli (saha operasyonu)
├── Merge: Conflict'i kullaniciya goster, secim yaptir
├── Field-Level Merge: Farkli alan degistiyse otomatik merge

Varsayilan: Server-Wins + kullanici bildirimi
```

