## BLE (Bluetooth Low Energy)
```csharp
// Cihaz tarama ve baglanti
public class BleDeviceService
{
    private readonly IBluetoothLE _ble;

    public async Task<IDevice> ConnectAsync(Guid deviceId, CancellationToken ct)
    {
        var adapter = _ble.Adapter;
        adapter.ScanTimeout = 10000;
        var device = await adapter.ConnectToKnownDeviceAsync(deviceId, cancellationToken: ct);
        return device;
    }

    public async Task<byte[]> ReadCharacteristicAsync(IDevice device, Guid serviceId, Guid charId)
    {
        var service = await device.GetServiceAsync(serviceId);
        var characteristic = await service.GetCharacteristicAsync(charId);
        return (await characteristic.ReadAsync()).data;
    }
}
```

## Platform-Specific Optimization

### Android
```
├── Startup: SplashScreen + lazy initialization
├── Memory: Bitmap recycling, WeakReference for images
├── Battery: WorkManager for background sync (respect Doze mode)
├── Lifecycle: OnStop'da sync durdur, OnResume'da devam
```

### iOS
```
├── Startup: NativeAOT for faster launch
├── Memory: NSAutoReleasePool for native objects
├── Battery: BGTaskScheduler for background processing
├── Lifecycle: SceneDelegate lifecycle'a uy
```

## Blazor Hybrid (MAUI 9)
```xml
<!-- MAUI sayfası icinde Blazor component -->
<BlazorWebView HostPage="wwwroot/index.html">
    <BlazorWebView.RootComponents>
        <RootComponent Selector="#app" ComponentType="{x:Type local:Main}" />
    </BlazorWebView.RootComponents>
</BlazorWebView>
```
- Web + Native UI mix: Blazor for forms/data, MAUI for native features
- Shared components: Razor Class Library ile web ve mobile paylas
- .NET 9: Render mode detection, improved reconnection

## App Update Strategy
```
├── Minor update: In-app notification + store link
├── Major update: Force update screen (min version check)
├── Hotfix: CodePush / OTA (Blazor Hybrid bolumleri icin)
├── Version check: API /api/app/version endpoint
```

