```

## Anti-Pattern'ler
| Anti-Pattern | Dogru Yaklasim |
|---|---|
| Main thread'de network call | Async + background thread |
| Buyuk image bellekte | Thumbnail + lazy load |
| Sync her saniye | Delta sync + smart interval |
| Platform code ViewModel'de | Interface + DI |
| SQLite'da complex JOIN | Denormalize, simple queries |
